<p>For this article, I=E2=80=99ll select the topic Pose Estimation to explo=
re and choose associated research papers to study.</p>



<h2 id=3D"step_2_finding_research_papers_" class=3D"wp-block-heading">Step =
2: Finding research papers <a href=3D"https://developer.nvidia.com/blog/how=
-to-read-research-papers-a-pragmatic-approach-for-ml-practitioners/#step_2_=
finding_research_papers_" class=3D"heading-anchor-link"><i class=3D"fas fa-=
